name: Fallen Angel Canyon
description:
Introduction

Trip report describes a 20+ mile round-trip covering 2.5 days of travel. Backpacked and spent two nights in the canyons - went down three canyons for the long week-end, while exploring 2 new canyons, and also repeated another known canyon. Could be done as a long day-trip instead if you don't want to do all the canyons
